Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Merced Elementary School in the Municipality of Banate, Province of Iloilo, to Rufino Cabangal Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 814
An Act Changing the Name of the Merced Elementary School in the Municipality of Banate, Province of Iloilo, to Rufino Cabangal Memorial School
Section 1. The name of the Merced Elementary School in the Municipality of Banate, Province of Iloilo, is changed to Rufino Cabangal Memorial School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
